lt beveled enclosures, creating the illusion of a 3D cube. You can assemble these three little scenes into any number of narratives; pick one that floats your boat.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Hot Soaks For Wart Treatment</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/hot-soaks-for-wart-treatment/</link><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/hot-soaks-for-wart-treatment/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;One of my kids came back from the dermatologist&amp;rsquo;s office where they were amused by the pamphlets with details about every possible skin condition. The title of one pamphlet became the prompt for this drawing.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Big Valve</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/big-valve/</link><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/big-valve/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dream | Larry King Officiates A Wedding In The City Of Giant Pipes</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dream-larry-king-officiates-a-wedding-in-the-city-of-giant-pipes/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 Jan 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dream-larry-king-officiates-a-wedding-in-the-city-of-giant-pipes/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Recursive Pipe Paintings</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/recursive-pipe-paintings/</link><pubDate>Thu, 22 Jul 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/recursive-pipe-paintings/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Started making paintings on paper of these giant pipes waiting to be buried. It wasn&amp;rsquo;t that interesting, but then I thought of making paintings of the pipes &lt;strong&gt;on the pipes.&lt;/strong&gt; No audience except maybe a few construction workers, and whoever digs up the pipes in some future century.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dead Dad Dream #3 | Shaving Sasha</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dead-dad-dream-3-shaving-sasha/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dead-dad-dream-3-shaving-sasha/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Big Tank</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/big-tank/</link><pubDate>Sat, 27 May 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/big-tank/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Fish And Skulls Under Old Washington Street El, Boston, 1985</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/fish-and-skulls-under-old-washington-street-el-boston-1985/</link><pubDate>Sun, 20 Feb 2011 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/fish-and-skulls-under-old-washington-street-el-boston-1985/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Good old &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I2GZrEhYyT40"&gt;Harry The Greek&amp;rsquo;s&lt;/a&gt;, where I got my first pair of safety shoes. &lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
In the background: Dudley Station on the old Orange Line elevated line. The platforms were made of wood, and a &amp;ldquo;Let&amp;rsquo;s Make Every Day Safe Driving Day&amp;rdquo; billboard, featuring a &lt;a href="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/56/13/99/561399a883ee46ae8931506b3db157e2.jpg"&gt;likeness of Eisenhower&lt;/a&gt;, remained remarkably intact 30+ years on, probably because its location directly over the tracks made it vandal-proof.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
The photo was taken during a big sewer main upgrade project which turned loose an unbelievable number of rats.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dream | A 50 Pound Bag Of Photoshop</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dream-a-50-pound-bag-of-photoshop/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 Jan 2010 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dream-a-50-pound-bag-of-photoshop/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;and yes, I did make the image in photoshop&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>5 Dreams (AIDS Quilt Bathroom Tiles)</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/5-dreams-aids-quilt-bathroom-tiles/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 1997 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/5-dreams-aids-quilt-bathroom-tiles/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Production art from &lt;a href="https://vimeo.com/showcase/5097789/video/228068003"&gt;5 Dreams&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Mister Zip With Moose And Stalin</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/mister-zip-with-moose-and-stalin/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 1992 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/mister-zip-with-moose-and-stalin/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Depressed Bathroom Selfie Somewhere In NYC</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/depressed-bathroom-selfie-somewhere-in-nyc/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 1987 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/depressed-bathroom-selfie-somewhere-in-nyc/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;I am overcome with empathy for this tired, bedraggled young fellow who was me. If you see him, please tell him he&amp;rsquo;s going to be OK. &lt;br&gt;
No idea where this institutional-looking bathroom was. All I know is that it was 1987, I was fresh out of school, and shooting Tri-X.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>